l calls: 12\n42\t- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 3, Grep: 2, Write: 1\n43\t- Largest Bash outputs: test:unit run (~50 lines), trace-id verbose test (~40 lines), coverage (~20 lines)\n44\t- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads\n45\t- Redundant operations: codeharness verify called twice\n46\t\n47\t### 4-4-source-isolation-enforcement — create-story (2026-04-03T01:05)\n48\t\n49\t- **Risk:** AC #4 depends on `templates/agents/evaluator.yaml` having `disallowedTools: [Edit, Write]` from story 3-2. Not verified that template exists.\n50\t- `/tmp/` path pattern is Unix-specific. Not a concern on darwin but noted for portability.\n51\t- All 9 ACs are test-provable (pure file system operations testable with real temp dirs).\n52\t\n53\t## Token Report\n54\t- Total tool calls: 12\n55\t- By tool: Read: 7, Grep: 3, Glob: 1, Write: 1\n56\t- Files read: 8 unique, 9 total reads (architecture-v2.md: 2 reads)\n57\t- Redundant operations: Two Grep calls to `source_access` could have been one\n58\t\n59\t### 4-4-source-isolation-enforcement — dev-story (2026-04-03T01:10)\n60\t\n61\tNone.\n62\t\n63\t## Token Report\n64\t- Total tool calls: 15\n65\t- By tool: Read: 5, Bash: 4, Grep: 4, Write: 2, Edit: 2, Glob: 2, Skill: 1\n66\t- Largest Bash outputs: coverage run (~160 lines), full test suite (~20 lines), tsc noEmit (~20 lines)\n67\t- Files read: 7 unique, 7 total reads\n68\t- Redundant operations: none\n69\t\n70\t### 4-4-source-isolation-enforcement — code-review (2026-04-03T01:18)\n71\t\n72\t**Bugs found:**\n73\t- HIGH: Path traversal via runId injection — unsanitized user input in file path. Fixed with `sanitizeRunId()`.\n74\t- HIGH: Silent file overwrite on basename collision — data loss. Fixed with `deduplicateFilename()`.\n75\t- MEDIUM: Stale workspace contamination from crashed runs. Fixed with pre-creation cleanup.\n76\t- MEDIUM: Missing edge case tests for sanitization, dedup, return shape. Fixed.\n77\t\n78\t**LOW (not fixed):** deduplicateFilename counter loop unbounded; hardcoded `/t